lot more atmosphere.

579
00:37:08,860 --> 00:37:12,520
And so I think here a situation
which is extreme,

580
00:37:12,520 --> 00:37:16,000
when we have sunrise
or sunset.

581
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:19,660
So the sun is there and the
light comes from this side and

582
00:37:19,660 --> 00:37:20,560
